name: Rocky The Flying Capybara
description:
You play as a capybara with rockets (these are only for flying), recharge them by eating, go through rough platforming to reach your friends that are relaxing at a hot spring.

The more you die the worse it gets!


Github : https://github.com/Rozwan/RockyTheFlyingCapybara

Known bugs : -hitting too many spears may stack uncanny;

-some sounds play more than they are supposed to.

Easy Mode : F3

No capybaras were hurt in making this game.
